                <item xml:id="addition1" n="1">
                  <p>Foll.<locus from="1" to="1">1</locus>,<locus from="8" to="8">8</locus>,<locus>23</locus>,<locus>24</locus>,<locus>63</locus>, and<locus>64</locus>are perhaps<date notBefore="0950">three centuries later</date>.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition2" n="2">
                  <p>Numerous diacritical points and marks of punctuation have been subsequently added throughout.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition3" n="3">
                  <locus from="1a" to="1a"/>
                  <p>On fol. 1 a there is a note, stating that the book belonged to<placeName>the convent of S. Mary Deipara:</placeName>
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܐܝܬܘܗܝ ܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ ܕܕܝܪܐ ܕܒܝܬ ܝܠܕܬ ܐܠܗܐ ܕܣܘܪ̈ܝܝܐ ܕܡܕܒܪܐ ܕܣܩܝܛܐ. ܟܠ ܕܡܦܩ ܠܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ ܡܢ ܕܝܪܐ ܗܕܐ ܐܘ ܟܐܡ ܥܠܘܗܝ ܘ܏ܫ</quote>.</p>
